{"word":"G4687 - σπείρω - speírō - spi'-ro - Sow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπείρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">speírō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">spi'-ro</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விதை, விதைக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to sow, scatter seed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably strengthened from <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a> (through the idea of <i>extending</i>); to <i>scatter</i>, that is, <i>sow</i> (literally or figuratively): - sow (-er), receive seed.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4586/4586\">G4586</a>, <a href=\"#/G4687/4687\">G4687</a>, <a href=\"#/G4690/4690\">G4690</a>, <a href=\"#/G4691/4691\">G4691</a>, <a href=\"#/G4701/4701\">G4701</a>, <a href=\"#/G4702/4702\">G4702</a>, <a href=\"#/G4703/4703\">G4703</a>"}]}